messages.message: Interesting. Did you try a different prompt with more explicit instructions, @peter?

yeah, i tried `give me a csv of all item names and prices` then `give me a csv of all item names and prices, with each item on a separate line`

the result was the same both times
```GREEN ONIONS, 0.79 AMANOYA HIMEMARU, 2.49 BINBIN RICE CRACKER, 0.09 CALBEE SHRIMP CHIPS, 1.99 CALBEE SHRIMP CHIPS, 1.99```
it also read the price wrong for some reason, binbin is 1.69 not 0.09

Interesting, I tried the sample with the meal receipts app.

The information on bin bin was correct here, although rest of the fields are either not available or wrong! @avi @Shubham :slightly_smiling_face:
Hi @Varun Jain, This is probably because of the model upgrade which is causing some changes in the results compared to what we were getting before.
Also, have you tried this only on the cropped image which has only the item details?
i did not, my full image is bigger. ill try the meal receipts app on my full pic :open_mouth:
(i didnt know that app existed, i never scrolled down enough)

meal receipts app results on my full image - left out some line items
```Receipt Item Details

(Quantity, Item, Total), (1, GREEN ONIONS, 79 F), (1, AMANOYA HIMEMARU MED, 2.49 F), (1, BINBIN RICE CRACKER, 9 F), (1, CALBEE SHRIMP CHIPS, 1.99 F), (1, CALBEE SHRIMP CHIPS, 1.99 F)```
if i crop to just the receipt, no table surrounding the receipt
```Receipt Item Details

(4068, GREEN ONIONS, 0.79), (AMANOYA HIMEMARU MED, 2.49), (BINBIN RICE CRACKER, 1.69), (CALBEE SHRIMP CHIPS, 1.99), (CALBEE SHRIMP CHIPS, 1.99)```
